# Dive & Underwater Camera Gear — Maintenance Log

**Owner:** Lorraine Roach, Coral Futures Institute (CFI-2020-047)
**Use:** Personal field-readiness log for the Kāneʻohe Bay Coral Resilience Study dives.
**Rule I actually follow:** nothing goes in the water until its line in this table is current. The photographic record is only as good as the housing seal. I have lost exactly one morning of transects to a flooded port and I am not doing that again.

Permits the gear is logged under: DLNR SAP-2026-KNB-0114, NOAA HIMS-2025-0089.

